     $-----------------------------------------------------------------------        
     $ SAP2000 VERIFICATION EXAMPLE 1-001                                            
     $ FRAME - INCLINED MEMBERS (L-SHAPED FRAME WITH INCLINED RAFTER)                
     $ SECTION: RECTANGULAR 12X12 IN, BENDING ONLY (AMOD=1E3, A2=A3=0)               
     $   A=144 IN^2, I33=1728 IN^4, E=3600 KIP/IN^2                                  
     $ GEOMETRY (GLOBAL X-Z PLANE):                                                  
     $   NODE 1: (0,0,0)   - FIXED BASE                                              
     $   NODE 2: (0,0,120) - KNEE JOINT                                              
     $   NODE 3: (96,0,192)- ROLLER AT FREE END (UX RESTRAINED, UZ FREE)             
     $   NODE 4: (-48,0,120)- CANTILEVER TIP (NO BC)                                 
     $ MEMBERS:                                                                      
     $   EID 1: 1->2 (VERTICAL COLUMN, L=120)                                        
     $   EID 2: 2->3 (INCLINED RAFTER, L=120)                                        
     $   EID 3: 4->2 (HORIZONTAL CANTILEVER ARM, L=48)                               
     $ LOAD CASES (MULTIPLE):                                                        
     $   LC2: 10 KIP DOWNWARD AT NODE 4; 0.15 KIP/IN UDL ON FRAME 3                  
     $   LC3: JOINT MOMENT AT NODE 2; UDL ON FRAME 1 (TRIANGULAR 0->0.1667 KIP/IN)   
     $   LC4: PROJECTED UDL ON RAFTER (FRAME 2) -0.1667 KIP/IN (Z-PROJ)              
     $   LC5: LOCAL UDL ON COLUMN (FRAME 1) -0.1667 KIP/IN (LOCAL 2-DIR)             
     $   LC6: LINEARLY VARYING LOAD ON FRAME 2 (0.0 TO -0.0312 KIP/IN LOCAL)         
     $   LC7: POINT LOAD -15 KIP AT MIDSPAN OF FRAME 2 (LOCAL-2)                     
     $-----------------------------------------------------------------------        
